Run this command in your terminal in the directory OpenShot was downloaded to verify the SHA256 checksum:
  echo "6ac1c327783f84b15dce0fb82b129eec212b3d817597e531d6ba434fdba8e66d  OpenShot-v3.5.0-x86_64.exe" | shasum -a 256 --check

You should get the following output:
  OpenShot-v3.5.0-x86_64.exe: OK